  Star, Flame, Wind, Moon, ChefHat, BellRing, Package, List, Plus, Minus, Send, ShoppingBag, Database, Trophy, Stamp, Diamond, Crown, UserCheck, Lightbulb, UserPlus, Lock, Unlock, Image as ImageIcon, MessageCircle, Filter, CheckCircle2, Gift, Activity, TrendingUp, TrendingDown
